May be a black-and-white image of text that says 'J.Strelou True love demands nothing my darling. We could ive live in a small wooden cabin together and andI I would be happy with only a roof over our heads and your arms.'.

node.text:
You are my home,⠀
my happy place. 🍷⠀
(cr: @j.strelou)

user.full_name: B E A U   T A P L I N

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by poets of instagram on September 06, 2021 tagging @beautaplin. May be an image of text that says 'Maybe there is no such thing as happily ever after. Perhaps all loves are bound to endure some difficulty and hurt. But if I can wake up each morning and find there beside me a friend true friend then I could survive anything. And that is what you are to me. Beau Taplin A True Friend'.

node.text:
With you, I could survive anything 🖤⠀
(cr: @beautaplin)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by poets of instagram on September 06, 2021 tagging @vav.ava. May be an image of text that says 'i am softer with you. your presence like a wave like a balm i am my good behavior. i am my best self. because i love you, because i am loved by you. AVA.'.

node.text:
Did someone come to mind while you were reading this?⠀
(cr: @vav.ava)
